rComments: Prof was unclear in his expectations for assignments and exams & never had enough material to cover a 3h lecture. More than half the class was review from the previous week & all the new material is crammed into the last hour, often resulting in keeping us until 10PM. He means well but doesn't explain concepts well so i relied entirely on the book
